野否則會collapse，所以先有呢啲法例上既要求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e13c575c3097f23f7b9736ca60f32369a96052","tid":338754,"uid":19015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>天價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係天價會人人爭住入去做成功人士?</blockquote><br />\n話Auditor係成功人士真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nauditor既價值好難三言兩語講曬出黎比你聽<br />\n但有audit經驗既會計仔起碼人工高d同埋出去易比人請<br />\n因為佢地會知道點deal with 其他auditor,點做IPO同一般既financial planning<br />\n所以fg都會去做下audit先再跳去其他公司<br />\n有幾多人頂唔順跳返出黎你又知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\naudit人工基本上係倒金字塔,大老細人工先高<br />\n你頭果3-4年計返時薪都低都喊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實多人入行都只係代表佢地搵唔到其他工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: OT緊</blockquote></blockquote><br />\nOT O到壞左腦？<br />\n<br />\n有邊行唔係人工倒金字塔？有邊行唔係大老細人工先高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 非3大account grad，冇做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6018b2c99206055c38555f8fe262f26760b5551","tid":338754,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T00:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭兩年就話時薪低到喊<br />\n第3, 4年就唔算低啦人工升左成倍"},{"pid":"766017462ad29077044c12ffc90b731be00a1a0a","tid":338754,"uid":27495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"個個都話除返你個平均工時人工好低，做五年野升manager 有五皮一個月，重想點，成班戇鳩仔人云亦云。"},{"pid":"257f9b85920e0bad31899c49428cf289c1903065","tid":338754,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個都話除返你個平均工時人工好低，做五年野升manager 有五皮一個月，重想點，成班戇鳩仔人云亦云。</blockquote><br />\n睇你自己過唔過到自己果關囉<br />\n<br />\n有人第3,4年已經放曬d 野比人做<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆7,8點放工<br />\n返到屋企食完飯臨上床先打卡話岩岩放工<br />\n去到manager 位已經當正自己partner 咁<br />\n<br />\n有人真係識得audit, 就會做到仆街<br />\nmanager grade 都日日1,2am<br />\n咁計返開8小時制, 都只係$25k 一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做audit, 識得卸膊, 識得同其他m, sm 混熟<br />\n好過你真係識audit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9515a805584f0dfc86b3fc97b6b8ba58d48829","tid":338754,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:30:10.000Z","msg":"樓上有人話internal audit大作用過ex 點解?"},{"pid":"2fa1ae7ee50307f9f8115719d6c0291f3d47da09","tid":338754,"uid":48069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出份report俾客報稅/出annual report<br />\n係客眼中auditor只不過係收錢出report又要問埋晒多餘問題<br />\n講真有幾可會出qualified opinion<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多時上手跳船 ＝出qualified opinion</blockquote><br />\n但大家都知auditor好多時查唔到假數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係坑入面...<br />\n查唔到假數係真<br />\n但阻止director報大數都係真<br />\n<br />\n因為partner亂簽係有機會負刑責<br />\n即係坐監</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n總記得n年前做細，被人放逐東北搭直升機數牛數羊<br />\n<br />\n真係影完相一隻一隻數<br />\n<br />\n而家大陸人做fieldwork , 用無人機求奇影幾張，就當數完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n查唔查到，係睇咩人做</blockquote><br />\n好似係其他post都見過你講呢個Case <br />\n所以話D auditor 成撚日都以為自己偵探咁  <br />\n搭架直升機影埋相就以為自己check得好足?<br />\n大陸人要撚化你呀  將D牛呀羊呀 移去第二度/問人借番黎 湊夠數<br />\n等你班auditor搭哂直升機自high以為自己做足workdone 打哂飛機  <br />\n<br />\n仲有  人地用無人機有乜問題  我又唔信你搭直升機9影幾張 又會好過人地囉"},{"pid":"af9ef94d0428a1be5e9f45d7bd7d2b128821c1c8","tid":338754,"uid":57779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天價人工<br />\n<br />\n亦擁有所有行業中最癲同最痴線既工作量<br />\n<br />\n但做出黎D野好似無價值?</blockquote><br />\n天價人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e9b1a9288935e2b18f111ba46187c1771447c2","tid":338754,"uid":27495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個個都話除返你個平均工時人工好低，做五年野升manager 有五皮一個月，重想點，成班戇鳩仔人云亦云。</blockquote><br />\n睇你自己過唔過到自己果關囉<br />\n<br />\n有人第3,4年已經放曬d 野比人做<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆7,8點放工<br />\n返到屋企食完飯臨上床先打卡話岩岩放工<br />\n去到manager 位已經當正自己partner 咁<br />\n<br />\n有人真係識得audit, 就會做到仆街<br />\nmanager grade 都日日1,2am<br />\n咁計返開8小時制, 都只係$25k 一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做audit, 識得卸膊, 識得同其他m, sm 混熟<br />\n好過你真係識audit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊份工唔係同人混熟會過得生活啲？每個人手頭上嘅enagament都唔同，project management skill又唔同，個個老闆要求又唔同，o 唔ot係由好多因素構成。我唔明乜叫識audit會做到仆街。唔識先會做到仆街，錯又要改，又要清q。"},{"pid":"601e716d30bd9f77dc2f94271f453611c977e135","tid":338754,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:53:46.000Z","msg":"宜家客戶就坐住一個Auditor<br />\n黎左差唔多個幾月<br />\n日日係房飲茶, 上網, 剪指/腳甲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5948216c03a8257847113e47272bb719980de8c","tid":338754,"ui